---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <main class="flex-grow flex flex-col w-full bg-slate-950 py-20 px-6 sm:px-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto w-full">
      
      <header class="mb-12 border-b border-slate-800 pb-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-serif text-white mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-slate-400 font-light">Last Updated: March 24, 2026</p>
      </header>

      <section class="space-y-8 text-slate-300 leading-relaxed font-light text-sm sm:text-base">
        
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-serif text-white mb-3">1. Introduction</h2>
          <p>
            The Automated Solo ("we", "our", or "us") operates as an independent research laboratory and authority site dedicated to law firm automation. We are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-serif text-white mb-3">2. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">We adhere to a philosophy of "Privacy by Design" and minimize data collection to what is strictly necessary to run the site effectively.</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 marker:text-slate-500">
            <li><strong>Automatically Collected Data:</strong> Standard server logs, IP addresses, browser types, and anonymous analytics (e.g., pages viewed, time spent on site) to improve our content.</li>
            <li><strong>Voluntarily Provided Data:</strong> Email addresses and connection information if you choose to subscribe to our newsletter or contact us directly.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-serif text-white mb-3">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 marker:text-slate-500">
            <li>To operate and maintain the website.</li>
            <li>To track affiliate link performance and ensure accurate referrals.</li>
            <li>To send periodic research updates or newsletters (only if explicitly requested by you).</li>
            <li>To improve user experience and analyze website traffic.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-serif text-white mb-3">4. Affiliate Tracking and Cookies</h2>
          <p>
            We use affiliate links (such as those from AppSumo, PartnerStack, or independent SaaS providers) to fund our research. Clicking on an affiliate link will place a cookie on your browser strictly for the purpose of tracking referrals and commissions. We do not use intrusive third-party advertising networks to track your behavior across the web.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-serif text-white mb-3">5. Data Sharing</h2>
          <p>
            We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information to third parties. We may disclose information if required by law, or to protect the rights, property, and safety of our laboratory and users.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-serif text-white mb-3">6. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>
            If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: <a href="mailto:privacy@theautomatedsolo.com" class="text-emerald-400 hover:underline">privacy@theautomatedsolo.com</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

      </section>

    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>